Class ResourceDeduplicationTask.Job

  • java.lang.Object
    • ai.grakn.engine.postprocessing.ResourceDeduplicationTask.Job
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.process.computer.MapReduce<String,ConceptId,String,Long,Long>
    Enclosing class:
    ResourceDeduplicationTask

    public static class ResourceDeduplicationTask.Job
extends Object
implements org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.process.computer.MapReduce<String,ConceptId,String,Long,Long>
    The map-reduce job submitted to the GraknGraphComputer that scan the whole set of resources in the graph and reduces by eliminating duplicates. The key in the mapping phase is formed by a resource's value and it's resource type.

    borislav
